      <h1>Best 401(k) Providers for Small Business (2026) &mdash; Plans Compared</h1>
      <p class="article-intro">Offering a 401(k) is one of the most impactful decisions a small business owner can make. It helps attract and retain top talent, provides meaningful tax benefits for the company, and gives employees a clear path to retirement security. But choosing the right provider can feel overwhelming &mdash; there are dozens of companies competing for your business, each with different fee structures, investment menus, and levels of support. This guide compares the top 401(k) providers for small businesses in 2026, breaks down the fees you need to understand, and walks you through setting up a plan step by step. Use our <a href="/calculators/finance/401k-calculator/">401(k) calculator</a> to model how much your employees could accumulate over time.</p>
