    <h2>Top 401(k) Providers for Small Business Compared</h2>
    <p>The table below summarizes the eight best 401(k) providers for small businesses in 2026. We evaluated each on monthly cost, per-employee pricing, investment quality, payroll integration, and overall ease of use. Costs shown are typical for a plan with 10 to 50 employees.</p>

